Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.50,0:01:43.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡卡西老師
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.10,0:01:48.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳥之國的任務已經結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.90,0:01:50.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到此為止吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.30,0:01:53.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是這樣的話 鳴人怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.80,0:01:56.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部都是我這個隊長的責任
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.50,0:02:01.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忍者的任務往往伴隨犧牲
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.60,0:02:06.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 回村吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.80,0:02:24.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你認為他們真的會回去嗎 流
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.30,0:02:26.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.00,0:02:31.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我倒是比較在意那個帶面罩的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.10,0:02:35.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要我去跟蹤他們嗎 北辰
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.80,0:02:37.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用 還是我來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.20,0:02:39.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你回去彙報一下情況
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.10,0:02:40.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.80,0:02:48.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴人之死
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.20,0:03:05.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情況如何
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.40,0:03:10.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,餘下二人以及後來趕來匯合的一個
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.40,0:03:11.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在已經出了國境
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.30,0:03:14.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該在回木葉村的路上了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.50,0:03:16.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.20,0:03:20.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,潛入大名府的那個
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.00,0:03:23.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像已經被鷺大人處決了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.70,0:03:30.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好茶好茶
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.10,0:03:39.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這幫傢伙從剛才開始到底在幹嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.00,0:03:42.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看啊看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.40,0:03:44.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是柿子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.60,0:03:45.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你幹嗎啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.40,0:03:52.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.20,0:03:59.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,替身術
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.80,0:04:01.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼時候用的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.40,0:04:10.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,木葉的忍者們居然敢欺騙我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.30,0:04:35.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紅明大人 請出來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.90,0:05:23.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳥之國 謀士紅明
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.70,0:05:30.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,濫用國家謀士之權
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.10,0:05:36.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暗殺前代大名以及公主朱鷺
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.30,0:05:40.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且派遣部下裝扮成詛咒武士 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.87,0:05:42.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,專橫跋扈
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.40,0:05:46.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蠱惑人心 干涉朝政
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.60,0:05:49.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此等危及鷺大人大名之位 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.10,0:05:53.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,篡位害人之罪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.90,0:05:55.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天地難容
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.80,0:06:01.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此 賜你切腹自刎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.70,0:06:15.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此啊 是這樣的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.20,0:06:19.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,申子緒 你居然陷害我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.80,0:06:23.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真丟臉啊 紅明
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.00,0:06:27.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,武士就該有氣魄以死謝罪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.50,0:06:29.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,立即執行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.50,0:06:50.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切都結束了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.40,0:07:04.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎 怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.20,0:07:06.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是霧隱之術嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.10,0:07:08.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對 這是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.60,0:07:15.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別管這些 趕快殺了他
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.60,0:07:18.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上路吧 對不住了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.90,0:07:21.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.10,0:07:26.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 發生什麼事了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.00,0:07:36.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個就是詛咒武士嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.70,0:07:38.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,追
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.20,0:07:38.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別讓他跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.20,0:07:53.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們繼續追
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.30,0:07:55.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我先行一步
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.70,0:07:56.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有件事需要調查
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.10,0:07:57.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收到
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.20,0:08:14.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們果然是一夥的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.70,0:08:16.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢著
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.80,0:08:20.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們是那天晚上的…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.70,0:08:25.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幽靈的真面目 我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.20,0:08:28.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.80,0:08:30.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紅明
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.00,0:08:35.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,操縱詛咒武士的就是你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.60,0:08:40.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那天晚上
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.60,0:08:44.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是為了調查詛咒武士而去的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.60,0:08:46.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我覺得
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.40,0:08:50.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有那位大人會這樣做
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.90,0:08:51.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是不見棺材不掉淚啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.90,0:08:53.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就讓我來揭穿你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.90,0:08:57.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.20,0:09:01.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡卡西老師
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.40,0:09:02.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您剛才到那兒去了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.20,0:09:04.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下再解釋吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.70,0:09:05.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們趕快離開
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.70,0:09:11.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快 你們也跟上
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.80,0:09:12.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.80,0:09:14.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧 天天
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.60,0:09:16.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 寧次
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.30,0:09:18.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.00,0:09:20.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一直跟蹤我們的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.40,0:09:37.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然你不想出來的話
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.70,0:09:41.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通靈之術
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.40,0:09:44.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 卡卡西
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.80,0:09:47.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幫忙找出隱藏在這裏的忍者吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.20,0:09:49.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小事一樁
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.60,0:09:57.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 躲在這邊的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.50,0:10:00.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,捉迷藏的遊戲到此為止了 快出來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.60,0:10:04.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狗鼻子果然與眾不同啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.40,0:10:05.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來躲不了了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.00,0:10:08.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你總算肯現身了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.10,0:10:30.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏怎麼會有這樣的地道
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.40,0:10:33.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,據說大名為了能瞭解庶民們的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.50,0:10:38.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而開鑿了這條遍佈全國範圍的地道
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.00,0:10:40.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大名嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.50,0:10:43.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是說詛咒武士和大名有關咯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.20,0:10:47.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少不會是幽靈
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.40,0:10:53.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在過會兒 對方應該會自表身份的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.60,0:11:06.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,任務結束後
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.00,0:11:10.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,返回村子應該是被雇傭忍者們的常識吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.70,0:11:14.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,任務的初衷既然變了 那就另當別論了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.50,0:11:18.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次的任務疑點太多
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.10,0:11:22.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們過於干涉別國的內政了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.00,0:11:25.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不像狗一樣亂聞的話
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.70,0:11:27.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本來應該可以活著回去的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.90,0:11:30.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真抱歉 狗招你惹你了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.40,0:11:39.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,森羅萬象 防護之術
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.60,0:11:40.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.20,0:11:43.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.50,0:11:45.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.80,0:11:49.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道身體裏含有岩石的成份嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.80,0:11:52.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然已經知道這個國家的秘密了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.00,0:11:53.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就不能讓你們活著回去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.50,0:11:56.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像比較麻煩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.90,0:11:57.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.60,0:11:58.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你先走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.80,0:12:00.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其他的我一個人能夠應付
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.70,0:12:02.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊 那我先走一步了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.90,0:12:05.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,硬化 岩石戰車
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.00,0:12:09.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.10,0:12:13.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,影分身
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.80,0:12:17.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到此為止了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.20,0:12:19.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.10,0:12:22.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,引爆符
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.10,0:12:52.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該可以了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.40,0:12:56.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到這裏應該可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.50,0:12:58.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這聲音是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.50,0:13:08.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴…鳴人…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.10,0:13:12.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.70,0:13:14.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,詛咒武士的真面目
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.60,0:13:17.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是鷺大人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.60,0:13:51.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是…你到底是誰…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.20,0:13:55.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是鷺大人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.30,0:13:58.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切都是鷺大人做的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.10,0:14:05.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從那個站姿來看
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.10,0:14:08.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我確定就是鷺大人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.10,0:14:11.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實情況比較複雜
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.10,0:14:14.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你幹嗎啊 天天
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.60,0:14:17.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那為什麼不早點告訴我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.30,0:14:18.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有寧次
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.00,0:14:19.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你很早就知道是鳴人了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.90,0:14:21.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早就知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.20,0:14:24.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們怎麼能這樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.20,0:14:26.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可擔心死了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.00,0:14:29.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為一直有忍者在監視我們
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.60,0:14:36.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寧次 天天
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.90,0:14:37.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加快步伐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.10,0:14:39.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們被人跟蹤了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.90,0:14:50.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在返回鳥之國
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.50,0:14:52.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別被發現了 就現在
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.60,0:14:55.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.60,0:14:58.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.30,0:15:00.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是用替身把那人甩了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.80,0:15:02.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可那只是暫時性的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.00,0:15:09.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.10,0:15:11.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從刑場追詛咒武士開始
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.90,0:15:13.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另一個人又跟了上來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.20,0:15:17.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.90,0:15:19.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有我一個人知情
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.60,0:15:21.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是白提你們操心了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.80,0:15:24.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道是你代替鷺大人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.70,0:15:26.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.90,0:15:29.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那鷺大人平安無事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.90,0:15:31.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大叔 你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.70,0:15:34.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓你們擔心了 哪個可惡的申子緒
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.20,0:15:38.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嚴刑拷打逼我認罪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.00,0:15:42.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大叔 你受了很多罪吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.80,0:15:45.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來龍去脈 進去以後再說
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.70,0:15:47.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鷺大哥等著呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.30,0:15:57.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,硬化 岩吹雪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.60,0:16:05.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們流浪忍者
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.90,0:16:09.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有歸屬之地 四處輾轉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.50,0:16:13.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偷學各村忍術精髓 創造屬於自己的招式
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.40,0:16:17.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比如說這招
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.70,0:16:21.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.10,0:16:24.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寫輪眼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.30,0:16:28.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,硬化 砂縛樞
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.00,0:16:32.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙 居然連我愛羅的忍術也…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.80,0:16:36.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,硬化 砂瀑送葬
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.70,0:16:45.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鷺大哥
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.70,0:16:49.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千島大哥情況如何
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.90,0:16:51.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.60,0:16:54.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經沒有生命危險了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.20,0:16:57.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在在我府邸的醫療室接受治療
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.90,0:16:58.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正在休息當中
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.10,0:17:06.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.50,0:17:08.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千島他怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.60,0:17:10.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰…是誰幹的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.90,0:17:11.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紅明
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.40,0:17:13.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誤會你了 真是抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.20,0:17:16.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小人實在承受不起
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.80,0:17:22.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是千島他拼了命前來告訴我實情的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.20,0:17:25.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個時候
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.70,0:17:33.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如今卻不能讓知道一切的你活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.90,0:17:38.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,私闖大名府 你已經是死罪了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.30,0:17:41.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.70,0:17:43.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鷺大人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.00,0:17:45.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千島
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.70,0:17:46.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大哥
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.20,0:17:52.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是飛鏢所傷
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.90,0:17:54.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趕快去御醫那裏
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.20,0:17:57.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鷺大人 請聽我說
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.30,0:17:59.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,申子緒大人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.40,0:18:02.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 申子緒背叛了你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.70,0:18:03.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.50,0:18:09.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暗殺你父親和妹妹的也是他啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.00,0:18:17.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他指派自己的親信忍者使用近衛兵的飛鏢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.60,0:18:19.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目的是嫁禍給紅明大人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.60,0:18:21.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紅明大人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.90,0:18:24.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定是被申子緒給暗算了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.20,0:18:26.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撐住啊 千島
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.00,0:18:29.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鷺大人 拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.90,0:18:33.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趕快停止紅明大人的處刑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.10,0:18:35.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再不去就晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.50,0:18:38.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以停止
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.60,0:18:40.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.90,0:18:44.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果讓申子緒發現我已經知道真相了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.70,0:18:46.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就無法復仇了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.00,0:18:48.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道你為了復仇
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.10,0:18:50.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不惜犧牲任何人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.50,0:18:51.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我能如何
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.70,0:18:54.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紅明被申子緒的心腹看守著
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.10,0:18:56.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是貿然出手
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.90,0:18:58.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們更本沒有任何勝算
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.40,0:18:59.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那讓我去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.00,0:19:02.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一個人去救紅明大叔
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.50,0:19:04.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣你該沒意見了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.80,0:19:06.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鷺大人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.40,0:19:11.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隨便你怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.20,0:19:16.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後我就假扮了詛咒武士
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.40,0:19:20.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我自己扮成詛咒武士
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.70,0:19:22.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為的是尋找暗殺父親的真凶
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.40,0:19:49.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是非但沒有找到兇手 紅明…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.90,0:19:53.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反而卻成了陷害你的道具
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.20,0:19:59.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直覺得那天的詛咒武士就是您
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.00,0:20:06.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才去了詛咒武士一度消失的寺廟
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.30,0:20:12.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後就遇到了詛咒武士
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.90,0:20:15.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是那個詛咒武士並不是我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.00,0:20:18.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該是申子緒叫人偽裝的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.00,0:20:20.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切都明瞭了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.40,0:20:22.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是申子緒那個老頭搞的鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.90,0:20:25.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,申子緒這個老匹夫
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.00,0:20:27.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道想先除了我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.70,0:20:32.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後再謀害鷺大人篡位嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.10,0:20:35.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個老頭居然還假惺惺的裝好人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.40,0:20:37.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真想揍他一頓
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.00,0:20:39.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴人還有各位 辛苦你們了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.90,0:20:40.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.50,0:20:45.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從現在開始 一切都交給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.10,0:20:47.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.20,0:20:48.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仇恨
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.80,0:20:51.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我一個人去了結吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.30,0:20:57.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不能復仇
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.40,0:21:00.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我心中的表
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.30,0:21:03.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仍然只會停留在過去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.41,0:22:42.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一個人能幹嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.13,0:22:45.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算你想復仇
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.15,0:22:48.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可人死不能複生
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.34,0:22:50.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使如此 你還執著於復仇嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.95,0:22:53.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣做能讓你快樂嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.34,0:22:56.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼做
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.74,0:23:01.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的父親和妹妹真的會高興嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.30,0:23:02.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集 
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.11,0:23:04.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靜止的時間
